      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lisle%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "The Tioughnioga River runs through Lisle, and Whitney Point Lake sits just east of the eastern town line.",
